Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.87,0:01:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陌生的恋情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我们的旗舰梅尔巴里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.27,0:01:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该知道吧  泰勒舰长?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.60,0:01:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正外面是外太空  我不会逃也不会吵闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会以轻松的心情  等待这场战争的结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.24,0:02:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尔康帝国\N从来就没有让俘虏留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.55,0:02:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个我已经听春美小姐说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知会被杀死  你故意来当俘虏…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.62,0:02:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.19,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天下有名的特姆舰长  假如要杀我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.13,0:02:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就把我干掉了  不会千里迢迢去抓我当俘虏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.96,0:02:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦的!  这种事  连傻瓜都懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.62,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就是让特南舰队全灭的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是驱逐舰微风号的舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.99,0:02:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰斯迪．植木．泰勒少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人不能相信  还是在流鼻涕的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不出是舰长的料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么大家都会这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很失礼  阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要因泰勒的外观而受到迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.67,0:03:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别看他这样…\N具有很多谋略  是了不起的策士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.01,0:03:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说他是具有很多谋略的策士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.68,0:03:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么  我总是会打胜仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.68,0:03:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…这就要小心啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.71,0:03:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最少给我吃饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在三更半夜皇帝偷吃东西这事被人知道的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会留下耻辱一辈子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.44,0:04:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是肚子这么饿  已经无法再忍耐下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所幸只有料理长一个人在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.78,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!既然这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.78,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有像山这么多  你老实说肚子饿就行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.89,0:05:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此事绝对不得宣扬出去  知道了没有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.82,0:05:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可是你讲话的方式好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你经常都这样子说话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这家伙还不知道我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  不要去理他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…不知道的话  这样反而方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.14,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吃了吗?你不是肚子饿吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.45,0:06:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常美味  不愧是梅尔巴的料理长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.19,0:06:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了  肚子饿时  什么都很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理长  我要再一碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我带你看舰内\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是舰不如说是庞大的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你不知道?\N嗯!请告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.52,0:06:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…竟然能干到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是来这首都舰不久的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是广大而已  几乎没什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.76,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是士兵的慰劳室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也头一次来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的啊  这个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.96,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…这里是我的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的故乡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.00,0:08:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我忘了问你的名字叫什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿萨琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是阿萨琳的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以摸一摸吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是饭后清口的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,培哥培哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我饲养的宠物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宠物?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  到这边来  我是阿萨琳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我呀  忘记了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,培哥培哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是!不要逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.85,0:11:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  是我呀  培哥培哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫培哥培哥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到你那边去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!  料理长  把它抓起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么?  会跑掉啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.22,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我办好啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!不要跑!培哥培哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.89,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你等我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.59,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有底的沼泽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会沉下去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  可以站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦  培哥培哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!也会下雨呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿萨琳你们的别墅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.60,0:13:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在前面的地方  反正要躲雨  我们就去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.31,0:13:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也\N怎么啦?料理长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别墅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愿去别墅吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.41,0:13:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么不愿意和我一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的话!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到啦…可是雨也停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的别墅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请到里面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.45,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿萨琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿萨琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  阿萨琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是…已经…不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.82,0:16:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…不…我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿萨琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…轻松一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.88,0:18:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多讨厌的事  就有很多喜欢的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的脸孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!女孩子还是笑的时候最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子…吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家很担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.26,0:19:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个赐给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们也回去吧  料理长大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.84,0:19:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫泰勒的这个男人  表面虽然呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.84,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却是把特南提督灭亡的猛将
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.28,0:19:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这男人杀一儆百处刑的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.02,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以把拉尔康帝国的士气更加的提高!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你就是泰勒吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.71,0:20:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属于惑星联合宇宙军驱逐舰微风号舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.05,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰斯迪．植木．泰勒少校  二十岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.22,0:20:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下!俘虏只有一死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.39,0:20:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们神圣拉尔康帝国不能更改的法规!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旺克…这个人不杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.74,0:20:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是!呃!说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不杀?\N究竟为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不杀  要做为我的宠物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.75,0:21:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是对可恨的惑星联合宇宙军的惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.39,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚?\N但是  陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.76,0:21:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦!旺克!已经决定的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.10,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他取名为八哥八哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令你给予我的宠物应有的待遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵…遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给这家伙最高的待遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.79,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做为皇帝陛下宠物最适当的待遇
